      Dead Effect 2is the newest addition to the  acclaimed  Dead  Effect
      franchise.  This  action  sci-fi shooter  is looking  to  push  the
      boundaries  of  first-person  shooters  to new  levels  with  slick
      graphics, rich narrative and RPG elements. Play  the  single-player
      missions at your own pace or engage your friends in the cooperative
      or PvP multiplayer mode. Train, develop your character, collect and
      upgrade countless weapons, gear and body implants and  take control
      of the monster-infested ship.
